155
00:46:55,200 --> 00:46:57,191
Pobre señorita.

156
00:46:58,160 --> 00:47:00,037
Señora.

157
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:02,878
Sra. McBain.

158
00:47:03,040 --> 00:47:05,873
